>  [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/includes/deprecatedcontent-md.md)]  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="28783-103">Um <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity> gerencia a execução de suas atividades filho utilizando <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext> métodos e eventos definidos na classe de <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> classe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="28783-103">A <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity> manages the execution of its child activities using <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext> class methods and events defined on the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> class.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="28783-104">Por exemplo, uma atividade filho é agendada para execução usando o <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext.ExecuteActivity%2A> de <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="28783-104">For example, a child activity is scheduled for execution using the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext.ExecuteActivity%2A> of <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="28783-105">Um <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity> atividade pode ser notificada quando uma atividade filho conclui sua execução assinando o <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Closed> evento definido em <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="28783-105">A <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity> activity can be notified when a child activity completes its execution by subscribing to the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Closed> event defined on <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="28783-106">O tempo de execução do fluxo de trabalho impõe determinadas restrições sobre <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity> execução, os mais fundamentais que é que um <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity> atividade não é possível mover para o <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Closed> estado se todas as atividades filhos são ainda em uma <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Executing>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Canceling>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Compensating>, ou <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Faulting>, estado.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="28783-106">The workflow runtime enforces certain constraints on <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity> execution, the most fundamental of which is that a <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity> activity cannot move to the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Closed> state if any child activities are still in a <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Executing>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Canceling>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Compensating>, or <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.Faulting>, state.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="28783-107">Este exemplo mostra um basic `CompositeActivity` que executa sua primeira atividade filho para execução.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="28783-107">This example shows a basic `CompositeActivity` that executes its first child activity for execution.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="28783-108">Quando a atividade filho é movido para o estado fechado, a atividade de composição é notificada e, em seguida, conclui sua execução.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="28783-108">When the child activity moves to the Closed state, the composite activity is notified and then completes its execution.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
public class HasOneChildActivity : CompositeActivity  
{  
    protected override ActivityExecutionStatus Execute(ActivityExecutionContext executionContext)  
    {  
        Activity child = this.EnabledActivities[0];  
        child.Closed += this.ChildClosed;  
        executionContext.ExecuteActivity(child);  
  
        return ActivityExecutionStatus.Executing;  
    }  
  
    void ChildClosed(object sender, ActivityExecutionStatusChangedEventArgs e)  
    {  
        e.Activity.Closed -= this.ChildClosed;  
        ActivityExecutionContext executionContext = sender as ActivityExecutionContext;  
  
        executionContext.CloseActivity();  
    }  
}  
```
